# Gemini API Key for AI features (Eco-tips, Carbon Calculator)
# Get one at: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here

# Note: Firebase configuration is currently loaded from firebase-applet-config.json
# Firebase client keys are generally safe to be public, but if you prefer to use env vars,
# you can update src/firebase.ts to use VITE_FIREBASE_API_KEY etc.
